jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Ti%C3%AAn-Vu-kinh-tri%E1%BB%87u-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-1wv7XLhCc9BTJcQIyiT4RQ">Phụng tặng Tiên Vu kinh triệu nhị thập vận - 奉贈鮮于京兆二十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nh%E1%BB%AF-D%E1%BB%B1c/T%E1%BA%A1-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%E1%BA%ADn-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-hu%E1%BB%87-%C4%91%E1%BB%9Bi-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-iJSArNLYdkHUT-P4FPcbig">Tạ Nguyễn Vận Đồng huệ đới kỳ 1 - 謝阮運同惠帶其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nh%E1%BB%AF-D%E1%BB%B1c/author-Gb-Ht5DceR7EDVtjdSr3Zw">Phạm Nhữ Dực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-B%E1%BA%A3o-Thoa-%C4%91%C3%ADch-thi/poem-61oOSvzFcyY_N0dc8Urb4Q">Tiết Bảo Thoa đích thi - 薛寶釵的詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-%C4%90i%E1%BB%83n-Thi%E1%BA%BFt-t%E1%BB%B1-Thi-Ch%C3%A2u-quy/poem-Wtg7pr18QYwpC7wnveu-vw">Trịnh Điển Thiết tự Thi Châu quy - 鄭典設自施州歸</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
